MobileWorks,is,a,crowd,sourcing,platform,that,has,a,pool,of,people,to,complete,tasks,such,as,translating,content,proofreading,articles,classify,data,and,tag,images,for,users,who,have,tasks,that,can,be,done,remotely,They,state,they,are,using,crowd,sourcing,to,put,the,underemployed,to,work,The,MobileWorks,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,interact,with,the,MobileWorks,platform,The,main,API,methods,are,posting,jobs,and,editing,job,information,to,the,MobileWorks,platform,receive,answers,about,jobs,and,find,out,what,the,status,of,a,job,is